    <output type="docs">projects/spaarke-ai-platform-chat-routing-redesign-r1/architecture/playbookconsumer-matchconditions.schema.json</output>
    <output type="docs">notes/handoffs/028a-bff-publish-delta.md</output>
  </outputs>

  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion testable="true">`IConsumerRoutingService.ResolveAsync` returns matching `sprk_analysisplaybook` system PK GUID per FR-1R-02.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Resolution algorithm matches FR-1R-03 — unit test covers each tiebreak path (consumerCode-specific over `default`; env-specific over `*`; priority asc).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Match-conditions JSON parsed per FR-1R-04 — unit tests cover null, empty `{}`, string equality, array in-list, multi-key ALL-match.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">5-min TTL per-tenant cache implemented; cache key includes tenantId + consumerType + consumerCode + env + matchKeyHash; unit test confirms cache hit on second call within TTL.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Change-tracking subscriber registered for `sprk_playbookconsumer`; cache invalidates within 30s of Dataverse update (unit test confirms invalidation; manual smoke verifies 30s budget post-deploy).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">DI registration in `AiModule.cs` is Scoped per ADR-010; no `IServiceProvider.GetService&lt;T&gt;()` in endpoint signatures.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">JSON schema at `architecture/playbookconsumer-matchconditions.schema.json` (Draft 2020-12) matches FR-1R-04.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">ADR-015 tier-1 logging preserved — no message/file content in routing logs; consumerType/Code/env/cacheHit/durationMs only.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">BFF publish-size delta reported; cumulative within NFR-01 (≤60 MB ceiling).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">code-review + adr-check exit 0.</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>

  <notes>
    Wave 1-K terminal sequential task — blocks 028b seed script + 028c/028d consumer migrations. Verify call-site list with grep before deciding whether `Services/Ai/PublicContracts/` re-export is needed; the consumers are CRUD-adjacent but the routing call is the cleanest point of injection. Use record-type for `IRoutingContext` to keep extension lean — Phase 4 may add `documentType` from classification metadata; design today for tomorrow's additions without breaking the contract.
  </notes>

